data.description: Have you ever wanted to live in a quiet, highly sought after area in Albertville close to all amenities including Sand Mountain Park, shopping, & restaurants?  This beautiful 3BR/3Bath home is now your opportunity!  Relax in the spacious living room w/ wooden, vaulted tongue & groove ceiling & centerpiece fireplace or prepare meals in the spacious kitchen.  Primary bedroom features en suite bathroom w/ step in shower & soaking tub.  Loft area provides a perfect area for a home office & has private deck. Basement is perfect for a flex space, has a private bathroom, and provides  access to the backyard.  In-ground pool, pool house, and privacy fenced yard round out homes features.
